StackBlitz link:  https://stackblitz.com/edit/components-issue-u6e7fj
Steps to reproduce:
1. apply theme in styles.scss
2. look at the result on a primary button


### Expected Behavior

Button contrast should work

### Actual Behavior

Button contrast doesn't work

